item.title: About
item.dc:creator: TJ Maynes
item.description: Hi, my name is TJ Maynes and I’m a Senior Software Engineer @VMwareTanzuLabs. I’m interested in Spring, Golang, Kubernetes, Nix, and Cryptocurrency. Currently, I’m spending more working in the Spring Cloud ecosystem, working on passing the Certified Kubernetes Administrator exam, and planning a wedding. This blog is place for me to give updates to what I’m working on and learning, if you have questions, or concerns, feel free to message me.
